Web application for learning latvian numbers and dates.

Currently has a functional view for writing Latvian numbers. 
It is able to parse the user's input and respond whether the written words correspond to the requested number.
It should cover all possible ways of writing numbers from 0 to 999999 in masculine gender.
It is able to detect when a wrong number is written and will give appropriate feedback.

A g4 source written in ANTLR defines latvian number grammar.

Staging environment present in: http://valoda.herokuapp.com/
